    "MiniGPT-4 [29] attributes the advanced multimodal generation capabilities of GPT-4 [1] to its integration of more sophisticated LLMs.",
    "To achieve similar capabilities, it employs a single linear projection layer to align the pretrained ViT [8] and Q-Former [15] with a frozen Vicuna [6]."
